ailed to make it out of her semi-final but Woods did.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mallory Franklin\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the third Briton\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And come the final she took the lead.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions The best destinations and activities to book this winter She was knocked off course at the first upstream gate by Angele Hug, much to the delight of the French crowd only for Australia's Noemie Fox to take the lead.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9598127498105963, \"rank\": 0.03709555815332042, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9657732343655211, \"rank\": 0.03443602724505299, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid